  <summary>Download and apply wallpapers from popular online sources</summary>
  <description>
    <p>View wallpapers from popular online sources (only Bing Wallpaper of the Day is currently supported), save them and set them as your desktop wallpaper.</p>
    <p></p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <p>\tAutomatically update a list of available wallpapers, on a schedule.</p>
    <p>\tAutomatically apply, on a schedule, the latest wallpaper available from any source.</p>
    <p>\tAutomatically apply the latest wallpaper when starting up the application.</p>
    <p>\tSave any image to a location of your choosing.</p>
    <p>\tRun in the background so that the app stays invisible, while continuing to do any of the scheduled tasks.</p>
  </description>

